snippet: Defending champion Andy Murray survived a scare to reach the quarter-finals of the men's Olympic tennis tournament with a three-set victory over Fabio Fognini on Thursday....
lead_paragraph: Defending champion Andy Murray survived a scare to reach the quarter-finals of the men's Olympic tennis tournament with a three-set victory over Fabio Fognini on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Tennis: Murray Reaches Quarter-Finals After Fognini Scare
headline.main: Tennis: Murray Reaches Quarter-Finals After Fognini Scare
